channel.title: Augustus - Veni Vidi Vici
channel.description:
[center][font=georgia][size=18pt][IMG]http://img215.imageshack.us/img215/1951/bannershield.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/a15wn.png[/img] Augustus is a Project created by [url=http://www.rune-server.org/members/compass_/]Me[/url] & [url=http://www.rune-server.org/members/shrugged/]Shrugged[/url] on R-S, It will be a project with full of content you don't see everyday. This will be hosted in the future. A big roll in Augustus will be the economy and the players roll of the server, as you have to rely on yourself to get what forfill your needs. Universal skilling and PvM will be implemented with ideas that have been never thought of. We will be at a professional state. And don't plan on getting this, as it won't ever be released.
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/0t0a1.png[/img] [url=http://www.rune-server.org/members/compass_/]Compass_[/url] - Client Developer [url=http://www.rune-server.org/members/shrugged/]Shrugged[/url] - Server Developer
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/HOqBR.png[/img] - Best Resizable & Fullscreen. - Great Loginscreen with many features.
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/7sK3a.png[/img] Name - Description - MM/DD __________________________________________________________
Artem - Removed sign folder Artem - Capitalized Client & Signlink classes Artem - Removed OnDemandFetcherParent & DummyClass Artem - Remplaced all lowMem booleans with only one. Artem - Started working on fullscreen * Changed the Jframe to be resizable. * Changed the process to be resizable. * Ripped Galkon's clientSize int & system. Artem - Music/Sound system implemented (Credits: Galkon) Artem - Started working on login Lobby * login Lobby base finished (Upon login) * Started Option tab lobby * Started & finished player tab lobby
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/3uxpf.png[/img] http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5DTNnjhs5p8
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/SpQEZ.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/yOUhV.png[/img] [img]http://imageshack.us/a/img856/9590/capture1va.png[/img] [img]http://img820.imageshack.us/img820/8452/captureptk.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/iGgZY.png[/img] Support Media soon to be released![/CENTER][/size][/font]
